<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Detention Assigned</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #c0392b;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background-color: #e67e22;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .detention-details {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-left: 4px solid #c0392b;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .important {
      background-color: #ffebee;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Detention Assigned</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{studentName}},</p>

      <p>A detention has been assigned to you. Please review the details below:</p>

      <div class="detention-details">
        <strong>Class:</strong> {{className}}<br>
        <strong>Week:</strong> Week {{week}}<br>
        <strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}
      </div>

      <div class="important">
        <strong>Action Required:</strong> You must book a detention time slot as soon as possible. Please log in to your student portal to book a convenient time.
      </div>

      <p>To book your detention time:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Log in to your student account</li>
        <li>Go to the Detentions page</li>
        <li>Select an available time slot</li>
        <li>Confirm your booking</li>
      </ol>

      <a href="{{bookingUrl}}" class="button">Book Detention Now</a>

      <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
      {{bookingUrl}}</p>

      <p><strong>Note:</strong> Failure to book and attend your detention may result in additional consequences. Please ensure you complete this detention as soon as possible.</p>

      <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please speak with your teacher or contact the KMC office.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>
      Kurt's Mathematics Centre Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} Kurt's Mathematics Centre. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated email, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
